The paper also involves training a neural network, which suggests that it could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper's focus on improving the performance of image captioning models suggests that it could also be relevant to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
